      ******************************************************************
      *           I D E N T I F I C A T I O N   D I V I S I O N        *
      ******************************************************************
       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
      ******************************************************************
      * PROGRAM NAME
      ******************************************************************
       PROGRAM-ID. ARR00205.
      ******************************************************************
      *                          ARQUITECTURA                          *
      ******************************************************************
      * DESCRICAO: Rotina que faz manutencacao ŗ tabela ART02_PERFIL   *
      *            dos perfis derivados quando feitas alteracoes no    *
      *            perfil master                                       *
      ******************************************************************
      *           L O G     D E     A L T E R A C O E S                *
      ******************************************************************
      *  INICIO  * AUTOR  * FIM    *  C O M E N T A R I O S            *
      *          *        *        *                                   *
      ******************************************************************
      *           E N V I R O N M E N T         D I V I S I O N        *
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                     CONFIGURATION SECTION                      *
      ******************************************************************
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
       SPECIAL-NAMES.
           DECIMAL-POINT IS COMMA.
      ******************************************************************
      *                      INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION                      *
      ******************************************************************
       INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
       FILE-CONTROL.
      ******************************************************************
      *                   D A T A   D I V I S I O N                    *
      ******************************************************************
       DATA DIVISION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                          FILE SECTION                          *
      ******************************************************************
       FILE SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                    WORKING STORAGE SECTION                     *
      ******************************************************************
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
       01  FILLER                      PIC  X(40) VALUE
           'INICIO WORKING-STORAGE DO ARR00205   '.
      ******************************************************************
      * PROGRAM CONTROL (PGM)
      ******************************************************************

      ******************************************************************
      * VARIAVEIS DE TRABALHO (VARTRAB)
      ******************************************************************
       01  WS-VARIAVEIS.
           05 WS-URL                PIC  X(12).
      ******************************************************************
      *            SWITCH
      ******************************************************************
       01  SW-SWITCH.
           05 SW-SELECT                  PIC X(01) VALUE SPACES.
              88 SW-NOT-FOUND                      VALUE '0'.
              88 SW-FOUND                          VALUE '1'.
      ******************************************************************
      * CONSTANTES
      ******************************************************************
       01  WC-CONSTANTES.
           05 CON-ARVT2002           PIC  X(10) VALUE 'ARVT2002'.
           05 CON-ARVT1000           PIC  X(10) VALUE 'ARVT1000'.
           05 CON-ARVT0200           PIC  X(10) VALUE 'ARVT0200'.
           05 WS-PROGNAME            PIC  X(10) VALUE 'ARR00205'.
      ******************************************************************
      * TABELAS
      ******************************************************************
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE ARCD2000 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE ARCD1000 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE ARCD0200 END-EXEC.
      ******************************************************************
      * COPYS
      ******************************************************************
           COPY ARCK0001.
           COPY ARCK0002.
           COPY VIAL0001.
           COPY VIAL0015.
           COPY VIAK0001.
           COPY VIAK0002.
           COPY VIAW0005.
           COPY VIAL0002.
      ******************************************************************
      * DB2
      ******************************************************************
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA END-EXEC.
      ******************************************************************
       01  FILLER                      PIC X(40) VALUE
           'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE ONLINE         '.

      ******************************************************************
      *                        LINKAGE SECTION                         *
      ******************************************************************
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
           COPY ETCL0002.
           COPY ARCL0205.
      ******************************************************************
      *              P R O C E D U R E   D I V I S I O N               *
      ******************************************************************
       PROCEDURE DIVISION USING ETCL0002-COMMAREA
                                ARCL0205-COMMAREA.
      ******************************************************************
      * CURSORES                                                       *
      ******************************************************************

           EXEC SQL
                DECLARE CURART01 CURSOR FOR
                 SELECT
                       CPERFIL
                     , GDESCRICAO
                     , INDPERM
                     , CPERFILM
                     , CUSERID
                     , HTIMEST
                 FROM ARVT2002_INFPERFIL
                 WHERE
                        CPERFILM = :ARCD2000-CPERFILM
                    AND INDPERM  = :ARCD2000-INDPERM
           END-EXEC.


      ******************************************************************
       0000-MAINLINE.
      *
           IF ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 1000-VALIDA-INPUT
                 THRU 1000-VALIDA-INPUT-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           IF ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
                 THRU 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           PERFORM 3000-FIM-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3000-FIM-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

       0000-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           GOBACK.

      ******************************************************************
       1000-VALIDA-INPUT.
      ******************************************************************

           IF ARCL0205-PERFILMAST    EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO ETCL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE ARCK0001-ERR-CPERFIL   TO ETCL0002-ST-ERRO
              MOVE ARCK0002-CAPLIC-AR     TO ETCL0002-CAPLIC-ERRO
           END-IF.
      *
           IF ARCL0205-CSEQUENCIA  EQUAL ZEROES
              MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO ETCL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE ARCK0001-ERR-CURL      TO ETCL0002-ST-ERRO
              MOVE ARCK0002-CAPLIC-AR     TO ETCL0002-CAPLIC-ERRO
           END-IF.
      *
       1000-VALIDA-INPUT-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.
      ******************************************************************

      * Cursor que traz os perfis derivados do master
           IF ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2100-ABRE-CURSOR
                 THRU 2199-ABRE-CURSOR-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           IF ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2300-FETCH
                 THRU 2399-FETCH-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2400-TRATA-CURSOR
                 THRU 2499-TRATA-CURSOR-EXIT
              UNTIL NOT DB2-OK OR NOT ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
           END-IF.

           IF ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2700-FECHA-CURSOR
                 THRU 2799-FECHA-CURSOR-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2100-ABRE-CURSOR
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2100-ABRE-CURSOR.
      *
           MOVE ARCL0205-PERFILMAST        TO ARCD2000-CPERFILM.
           MOVE ARCK0002-N-PERFIL-MASTER   TO ARCD2000-INDPERM.

           EXEC SQL
               OPEN CURART01
           END-EXEC

           MOVE CON-ARVT2002               TO ETCL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF NOT DB2-OK
                 MOVE '2100-ABRE-CURSOR' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
                 MOVE 'SQLCODE         ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
                 MOVE SQLCODE            TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
                      PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                         THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT

                 MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2   TO ETCL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2    TO ETCL0002-NR-ERRO
                                              ETCL0002-ST-ERRO
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2199-ABRE-CURSOR-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                2200-SELECT-ART02
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2200-SELECT-ART02.

      *   Faz SELECT ŗ tabela ART02 para trazer URL antigo
      *   Como rťplica do master, encadeamento ť igual para todos.
      *   Usado para o caso do UPDATE

           MOVE ARCD2000-CPERFIL           TO ARCD0200-CPERFIL
           MOVE ARCL0205-CSEQUENCIA        TO ARCD0200-CSEQUENCIA

           EXEC SQL
                 SELECT  CURL1
                       , CURL2
                       , CURL3
                       , CURL4
                       , CURL5
                 INTO   :ARCD0200-CURL1
                      , :ARCD0200-CURL2
                      , :ARCD0200-CURL3
                      , :ARCD0200-CURL4
                      , :ARCD0200-CURL5
                 FROM ARVT0200_PERFIL
                 WHERE CPERFIL = :ARCD0200-CPERFIL
                       AND CSEQUENCIA = :ARCD0200-CSEQUENCIA
           END-EXEC

           MOVE CON-ARVT0200               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
              EVALUATE TRUE
              WHEN DB2-OK
                 EVALUATE TRUE
                 WHEN ARCD0200-CURL1 NOT EQUAL SPACES
                    MOVE ARCD0200-CURL1          TO WS-URL
                 WHEN ARCD0200-CURL2 NOT EQUAL SPACES
                    MOVE ARCD0200-CURL2          TO WS-URL
                 WHEN ARCD0200-CURL3 NOT EQUAL SPACES
                    MOVE ARCD0200-CURL3          TO WS-URL
                 WHEN ARCD0200-CURL4 NOT EQUAL SPACES
                    MOVE ARCD0200-CURL4          TO WS-URL
                 WHEN ARCD0200-CURL5 NOT EQUAL SPACES
                    MOVE ARCD0200-CURL5          TO WS-URL
                 END-EVALUATE

                 SET SW-FOUND TO TRUE
              WHEN DB2-NOTFND
                 CONTINUE
              WHEN OTHER
                MOVE '2200-SELECT-ART02' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
                MOVE 'SQLCODE'          TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
                MOVE SQLCODE            TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
                PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                   THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT

                MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2  TO ETCL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2   TO ETCL0002-NR-ERRO
                                            ETCL0002-ST-ERRO
              END-EVALUATE
           END-IF.

       2299-SELECT-ART02-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2300-FETCH
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2300-FETCH.
      *
           EXEC SQL
              FETCH CURART01
              INTO
                  :ARCD2000-CPERFIL
                , :ARCD2000-GDESCRICAO
                , :ARCD2000-INDPERM
                , :ARCD2000-CPERFILM
                , :ARCD2000-CUSERID
                , :ARCD2000-HTIMEST
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-ARVT2002               TO ETCL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
              EVALUATE TRUE
              WHEN DB2-OK
              WHEN DB2-NOTFND
                 CONTINUE
              WHEN OTHER
                 MOVE '2300-FETCH'       TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
                 MOVE 'SQLCODE'          TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
                 MOVE SQLCODE            TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
                 PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                    THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT

                 MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2      TO ETCL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2       TO ETCL0002-NR-ERRO
                                                 ETCL0002-ST-ERRO
              END-EVALUATE
           END-IF.

       2399-FETCH-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                       2400-TRATA-CURSOR
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2400-TRATA-CURSOR.

           SET SW-NOT-FOUND TO TRUE.

           IF ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS AND ARCL0205-MANUT-UPDATE
           AND SW-NOT-FOUND
               PERFORM 2200-SELECT-ART02
                  THRU 2299-SELECT-ART02-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *  Chamada pela transacao em modo de update
           IF ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS AND ARCL0205-MANUT-UPDATE
               PERFORM 2500-UPDATE-ART02
                  THRU 2599-UPDATE-ART02-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *  Chamada pela transacao em modo de delete
           IF ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS AND ARCL0205-MANUT-DELETE
              PERFORM 2600-DELETE-ART02
                 THRU 2699-DELETE-ART02-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           IF ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2300-FETCH
                 THRU 2399-FETCH-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
       2499-TRATA-CURSOR-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                2500-UPDATE-ART02
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2500-UPDATE-ART02.

      *  Faz UPDATE ao perfil derivado caso a sequencia exista.
      *
           MOVE ARCD2000-CPERFIL           TO ARCD0200-CPERFIL
           MOVE ARCL0205-CSEQUENCIA        TO ARCD0200-CSEQUENCIA
           MOVE ARCL0205-CHIERAR1          TO ARCD0200-CHIERAR1
           MOVE ARCL0205-CURL1             TO ARCD0200-CURL1
           MOVE ARCL0205-CHIERAR2          TO ARCD0200-CHIERAR2
           MOVE ARCL0205-CURL2             TO ARCD0200-CURL2
           MOVE ARCL0205-CHIERAR3          TO ARCD0200-CHIERAR3
           MOVE ARCL0205-CURL3             TO ARCD0200-CURL3
           MOVE ARCL0205-CHIERAR4          TO ARCD0200-CHIERAR4
           MOVE ARCL0205-CURL4             TO ARCD0200-CURL4
           MOVE ARCL0205-CHIERAR5          TO ARCD0200-CHIERAR5
           MOVE ARCL0205-CURL5             TO ARCD0200-CURL5
           MOVE ARCL0205-USER              TO ARCD0200-CUSERID

           EXEC SQL
                UPDATE ARVT0200_PERFIL
                SET
                    CPERFIL = :ARCD0200-CPERFIL
                  , CSEQUENCIA = :ARCD0200-CSEQUENCIA
                  , CHIERAR1 = :ARCD0200-CHIERAR1
                  , CURL1 = :ARCD0200-CURL1
                  , CHIERAR2 = :ARCD0200-CHIERAR2
                  , CURL2 = :ARCD0200-CURL2
                  , CHIERAR3 = :ARCD0200-CHIERAR3
                  , CURL3 = :ARCD0200-CURL3
                  , CHIERAR4 = :ARCD0200-CHIERAR4
                  , CURL4 = :ARCD0200-CURL4
                  , CHIERAR5 = :ARCD0200-CHIERAR5
                  , CURL5 = :ARCD0200-CURL5
                  , CUSERID  = :ARCD0200-CUSERID
                  , HTIMEST = CURRENT TIMESTAMP
                 WHERE
                      CPERFIL = :ARCD0200-CPERFIL
                      AND CSEQUENCIA = :ARCD0200-CSEQUENCIA
           END-EXEC

           MOVE CON-ARVT0200               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
              EVALUATE TRUE
              WHEN DB2-OK
                IF ARCL0205-CURL1 NOT EQUAL SPACES
                OR ARCL0205-CURL2 NOT EQUAL SPACES
                OR ARCL0205-CURL3 NOT EQUAL SPACES
                OR ARCL0205-CURL4 NOT EQUAL SPACES
                OR ARCL0205-CURL5 NOT EQUAL SPACES
                   PERFORM 2510-VALIDA-URL
                      THRU 2519-VALIDA-URL-EXIT
                END-IF
              WHEN DB2-NOTFND
                CONTINUE
              WHEN OTHER
                MOVE '2500-UPDATE-ART02' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
                MOVE 'SQLCODE'          TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
                MOVE SQLCODE            TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
                PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                   THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT

                MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2  TO ETCL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2   TO ETCL0002-NR-ERRO
                                            ETCL0002-ST-ERRO
              END-EVALUATE
           END-IF.
      *
       2599-UPDATE-ART02-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2510-VALIDA-URL
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2510-VALIDA-URL.
      *
      *  VALIDA se URL ť novo, se for insere permissoes apenas de
      *  consulta. Permissűes para mais opcoes tem de ser configuradas
      *  na transacao de replica de perfil

           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN ARCL0205-CURL1 NOT EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE ARCL0205-CURL1          TO ARCD1000-CURL
           WHEN ARCL0205-CURL2 NOT EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE ARCL0205-CURL2          TO ARCD1000-CURL
           WHEN ARCL0205-CURL3 NOT EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE ARCL0205-CURL3          TO ARCD1000-CURL
           WHEN ARCL0205-CURL4 NOT EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE ARCL0205-CURL4          TO ARCD1000-CURL
           WHEN ARCL0205-CURL5 NOT EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE ARCL0205-CURL5          TO ARCD1000-CURL
           END-EVALUATE.
      *
           MOVE ARCD2000-CPERFIL           TO ARCD1000-CPERFIL

           EXEC SQL
                 SELECT  IBROWSE
                       , ICREATE
                       , IMODIFY
                       , IDELETE
                 INTO   :ARCD1000-IBROWSE
                      , :ARCD1000-ICREATE
                      , :ARCD1000-IMODIFY
                      , :ARCD1000-IDELETE
                 FROM ARVT1000_PERFIL_ACTIONS
                 WHERE   CPERFIL = :ARCD1000-CPERFIL
                     AND CURL = :ARCD1000-CURL
           END-EXEC

           MOVE CON-ARVT1000               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT

           IF ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
              EVALUATE TRUE
              WHEN DB2-OK
                 CONTINUE
              WHEN DB2-NOTFND
                 PERFORM 2520-INSERE-PERMISSOES
                    THRU 2529-INSERE-PERMISSOES-EXIT
              WHEN OTHER
                MOVE '2510-VALIDA-URL'   TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
                MOVE 'SQLCODE'          TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
                MOVE SQLCODE            TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
                PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                   THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT

                MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2  TO ETCL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2   TO ETCL0002-NR-ERRO
                                            ETCL0002-ST-ERRO
              END-EVALUATE
           END-IF.

       2519-VALIDA-URL-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2520-INSERE-PERMISSOES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2520-INSERE-PERMISSOES.
      *
      *  VALIDA se URL ť novo, se for insere permissoes apenas de
      *  consulta. Permissűes para mais opcoes tem de ser configuradas
      *  na transacao de replica de perfil

           MOVE ARCK0002-ACTION-ACESSO     TO ARCD1000-IBROWSE
           MOVE ARCK0002-ACTION-N-ACESSO   TO ARCD1000-ICREATE
           MOVE ARCK0002-ACTION-N-ACESSO   TO ARCD1000-IMODIFY
           MOVE ARCK0002-ACTION-N-ACESSO   TO ARCD1000-IDELETE
           MOVE ARCL0205-USER              TO ARCD1000-CUSERID

           EXEC SQL
              INSERT INTO
              ARVT1000_PERFIL_ACTIONS
                (  CPERFIL
                 , CURL
                 , IBROWSE
                 , ICREATE
                 , IMODIFY
                 , IDELETE
                 , CUSERID
                 , HTIMEST)
              VALUES ( :ARCD1000-CPERFIL
                     , :ARCD1000-CURL
                     , :ARCD1000-IBROWSE
                     , :ARCD1000-ICREATE
                     , :ARCD1000-IMODIFY
                     , :ARCD1000-IDELETE
                     , :ARCD1000-CUSERID
                     , CURRENT TIMESTAMP )
           END-EXEC

           MOVE CON-ARVT1000               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT

           IF ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
              EVALUATE TRUE
              WHEN DB2-OK
                 PERFORM 2530-VALIDA-URL-ANTIGO
                    THRU 2539-VALIDA-URL-ANTIGO-EXIT
              WHEN DB2-DUPREC
                 CONTINUE
              WHEN OTHER
                MOVE '2520-INSERE-PERMISSOES' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
                MOVE 'SQLCODE'          TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
                MOVE SQLCODE            TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
                PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                   THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT

                MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2  TO ETCL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2   TO ETCL0002-NR-ERRO
                                            ETCL0002-ST-ERRO
              END-EVALUATE
           END-IF.

       2529-INSERE-PERMISSOES-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                  2530-VALIDA-URL-ANTIGO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2530-VALIDA-URL-ANTIGO.

      *  Valida se URL antigo ť usado em mais alguma sequencia. Se for
      *  mantem registo na tabela ART10_PERFIL_ACTIONS, sen„o apaga

           MOVE WS-URL                     TO ARCD1000-CURL
           MOVE ARCD2000-CPERFIL           TO ARCD1000-CPERFIL

           EXEC SQL
              SELECT CSEQUENCIA
              INTO  :ARCD0200-CSEQUENCIA
              FROM   ARVT0200_PERFIL
              WHERE  CPERFIL = :ARCD0200-CPERFIL
                AND (CURL1  = :WS-URL
                 OR  CURL2  = :WS-URL
                 OR  CURL3  = :WS-URL
                 OR  CURL4  = :WS-URL
                 OR  CURL5  = :WS-URL)
              FETCH FIRST ROW ONLY
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-ARVT0200               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
              EVALUATE TRUE
              WHEN DB2-OK
                 CONTINUE
              WHEN DB2-NOTFND
                 PERFORM 2540-APAGA-PERMISSOES
                    THRU 2549-APAGA-PERMISSOES-EXIT
              WHEN OTHER
                MOVE '2530-VALIDA-URL-ANTIGO' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
                MOVE 'SQLCODE'          TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
                MOVE SQLCODE            TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
                PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                   THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT

                MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2  TO ETCL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2   TO ETCL0002-NR-ERRO
                                            ETCL0002-ST-ERRO
              END-EVALUATE
           END-IF.

       2539-VALIDA-URL-ANTIGO-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                  2540-APAGA-PERMISSOES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2540-APAGA-PERMISSOES.
      *
           MOVE WS-URL                     TO ARCD1000-CURL
           MOVE ARCD2000-CPERFIL           TO ARCD1000-CPERFIL

           EXEC SQL
                DELETE FROM
                ARVT1000_PERFIL_ACTIONS
                WHERE
                    CPERFIL = :ARCD1000-CPERFIL
                     AND CURL = :ARCD1000-CURL
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-ARVT1000               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF NOT DB2-OK
                MOVE '2540-APAGA-PERMISSOES'  TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
                MOVE 'SQLCODE'          TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
                MOVE SQLCODE            TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
                PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                   THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT

                 MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2   TO ETCL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2    TO ETCL0002-NR-ERRO
                                              ETCL0002-ST-ERRO
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2549-APAGA-PERMISSOES-EXIT.
           EXIT.


      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                  2600-DELETE-ART02
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2600-DELETE-ART02.
      *
           MOVE ARCD2000-CPERFIL           TO ARCD0200-CPERFIL
           MOVE ARCL0205-CSEQUENCIA        TO ARCD0200-CSEQUENCIA

           EXEC SQL
                DELETE FROM
                ARVT0200_PERFIL
                WHERE
                   CPERFIL = :ARCD0200-CPERFIL
                   AND CSEQUENCIA = :ARCD0200-CSEQUENCIA
           END-EXEC

           MOVE CON-ARVT0200               TO ETCL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
              EVALUATE TRUE
              WHEN DB2-OK
              WHEN DB2-NOTFND
                 CONTINUE
              WHEN OTHER
                MOVE '2699-DELETE-ART02' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
                MOVE 'SQLCODE'          TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
                MOVE SQLCODE            TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
                PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                   THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT

                 MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2   TO ETCL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2    TO ETCL0002-NR-ERRO
                                              ETCL0002-ST-ERRO
              END-EVALUATE
           END-IF.

       2699-DELETE-ART02-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2700-FECHA-CURSOR
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2700-FECHA-CURSOR.
      *
           EXEC SQL
              CLOSE CURART01
           END-EXEC.

       2799-FECHA-CURSOR-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      ******************************************************************
      * 3000-FIM-PROGRAMA
      ******************************************************************
       3000-FIM-PROGRAMA.
           CONTINUE.

       3000-FIM-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
            EXIT.
      ******************************************************************
      *                       AREA DE PROCEDURES                       *
      ******************************************************************
       COPY VIAP0015.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0099 END-EXEC.
